Shape.Text: High Level Personal Banking Onboarding Customer Journey Date: 27/04/2016 Version: 0.1

Shape.Name: Start/End
Shape.Text: Customer is exposed to marketing and searches or enters the Al Rayan Website Www. Alrayanbank.co.uk

Shape.Name: Process.6
Shape.Text: Customer decides that they would like to open a personal banking product

Shape.Name: Process.78
Shape.Text: Customer/advisor navigates to relevant personal banking product and clicks “Apply Now”

Shape.Name: Process.79
Shape.Text: CAA Form section 1 to present on screen

Shape.Name: Decision
Shape.Text: Does the customer already have an account?

Shape.Name: Process.86
Shape.Text: Customer to complete all fields within section 1 and click “Continue”

Shape.Name: Start/End.89
Shape.Text: Customer informed to apply via online banking: Please see Existing Online Application Process

Shape.Name: Decision.104
Shape.Text: Does the customer require more information about Al Rayan Products?

Shape.Name: Process.106
Shape.Text: Customer to submit “Call Back Request” form online

Shape.Name: Process.109
Shape.Text: Direct Sales team to call customer back

Shape.Name: Process.111
Shape.Text: Direct Sales team to talk the customer through the various products and assist them in making a decision

Shape.Name: Start/End.134
Shape.Text: Customer to call into the contact centre

Shape.Name: Process.136
Shape.Text: Customer to enquire about the range of products we offer

Shape.Name: Process.137
Shape.Text: Customer service agent to advise customer of products on offer

Shape.Name: Process.143
Shape.Text: Customer service agent to book a call back for the customer

Shape.Name: Start/End.150
Shape.Text: Customer to enter the branch and enquires about our range of products

Shape.Name: Process.152
Shape.Text: Seller to talk customer through range of products

Shape.Name: Start/End.156
Shape.Text: Customer to obtain application form from: - Branch - Online Website

Shape.Name: Process.160
Shape.Text: Customer will then complete and send the application form to Al Rayan Bank

Shape.Name: Process.161
Shape.Text: Application form to be received and checked

Shape.Name: Decision.164
Shape.Text: Has the application form been completed fully?

Shape.Name: Process.171
Shape.Text: Post room to distribute personal banking applications to Account Services

Shape.Name: Process.174
Shape.Text: Account Services to call the customer and ask for missing information. Missing information to be completed on application form.

Shape.Name: Subprocess.780
Shape.Text: Key Green – Branch Specific Processes Blue – Post Specific Processes Red – Contact Centre Specific Processes Black – Generic processes carried out by all
